# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# SAFETY DEFAULT: this repo publishes NO PDFs. It ships as Markdown only.
#
# Decision: the only papers being shared are the two reviews below, and they
# are shared as arXiv LINKS in the README (the free, legitimate versions) —
# NOT by hosting their copyrighted publisher PDFs:
#     • Krantz et al.,  A Quantum Engineer's Guide…    → arXiv:1904.06560
#     • Kjaergaard et al.,  Current State of Play       → arXiv:1905.13641
#
# Everything else in this folder is confidential (IQM report, vendor
# datasheets), copyrighted, internal lab setup, or personal (thesis / QE
# report) — so every PDF is blocked. Add a curated link to the README to
# "share" a paper; never commit the file.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Block every PDF + the standalone HTML so nothing sensitive is ever committed
*.pdf
*.html

# Your private "quantum hardware tutorial" slide deck — block the WHOLE folder,
# not just its PDFs, so images/pptx/etc. added there later can't leak either
quantum hardware tutorial/

# OS / editor cruft
.DS_Store
.vscode/
*.swp
